<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> ﴿سَلْسَبِيلًا﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>: حَدِيدَةُ <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span> الْجِرْيَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">﴿غَوْلٌ﴾:</span> وَجَعُ الْبَطْنِ <span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>﴿يُنْزَفُونَ﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(٤)</span>: لَا تَذْهَبُ عُقُولُهُمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ ﴿دِهَاقًا﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(٥)</span>: مُمْتَلِئًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>﴿كَوَاعِبَ﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(٦)</span>: نَوَاهِدَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الرَّحِيقُ:</span> الْخَمْرُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">التَّسْنِيمُ:</span> يَعْلُو شَرَابَ أَهْلِ الْجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">﴿خِتَامُهُ﴾:</span> طِينُهُ ﴿مِسْكٌ﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>﴿نَضَّاخَتَانِ﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(٨)</span>: فَيَّاضَتَانِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">يُقَالُ:</span> مَوْضُونَةٌ: مَنْسُوجَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> مِنْهُ:</span> وَضِينُ النَّاقَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالْكُوبُ:</span> مَا لَا أُذُنَ لَهُ وَلَا عُرْوَةَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالْأَبَارِيقُ:</span> ذَوَاتُ <span style="color:#008000">(٩)</span> الْآذَانِ وَالْعُرَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>﴿عُرُبًا﴾ <span style="color:#008000">(١٠)</span>: مُثَقَّلَةً وَاحِدُهَا: عَرُوبٌ مِثْلُ: صَبُورٍ وَصُبُرٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> يُسَمِّيهَا أَهْلُ مَكَّةَ:</span> الْعَرِبَةَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَهْلُ الْمَدِينَةِ:</span> الْغَنِجَةَ وَأَهْلُ الْعِرَاقِ: الشَّكِلَةَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الإنسان: ١٨].<br>(٢) عليه صح.<br>(٣) لأبي ذر وعليه صح: "بَطْنٍ".<br>(٤) [الصافات: ٤٧].<br>(٥) [النبأ: ٣٤].<br>(٦) [النبأ: ٣٣].<br>(٧) [المطففين: ٢٦].<br>(٨) [الرحمن: ٦٦].<br>(٩) لأبي ذر وعليه صح: "ذَاتُ".<br>(١٠) [الواقعة: ٣٧].</p> </div>